{"tid":1479080,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"又話不分化不割蓆","createTime":"2019-08-16T18:15:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-16T19:53:57.000Z","uid":128569,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"f8dfe47f61ed4a1d48d00f819c07f446b2f1fbdc","tid":1479080,"uid":128569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T18:15:08.000Z","msg":"見到隔離有post屌呢幾日和理非<br />\n做乜尻 我地從來無同前線手足割過蓆<br />\n我地嚟緊兩日要和理非係想俾政府、國際睇到我地仲有好多人撐<br />\n隔離有post就即刻話俾大台騎劫左<br />\n做咩要和理非<br />\n我知道到而家咩都無爭取到<br />\n而家只不過叫勇武抖一抖<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">絕對唔係叫佢地以後唔好出嚟</span><br />\n希望大家記得我地呢個運動開頭<br />\n全靠 不分化、不割蓆先會堅持到咁耐<br />\n818 維園見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"789959bb120d5f3058ebbe04f1b1e596b8cb861f","tid":1479080,"uid":86378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T18:22:04.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">818 2點 維園見<br />\n大家一定要出！</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/a14Krun.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fa14Krun.jpg&h=f12c1c4b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RkxLVot.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRkxLVot.jpg&h=9b3f8527&s={SIZE}\" /><blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Xg1EfoE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXg1EfoE.jpg&h=24a18478&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2vynXB0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2vynXB0.jpg&h=613c2f83&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gSvYvW0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgSvYvW0.jpg&h=a8c38726&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JRJLaW1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJRJLaW1.jpg&h=c